<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>About Us</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f0f4f8;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    header {
      background-color: #003366;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    section#about {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: white;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    h2 {
      color: #003366;
    }

    p {
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <h1>About Us</h1>
  </header>

  <section id="about">
    <h2>Who We Are</h2>
    <p>
      We are a passionate team of educators and developers who love to help beginners get started with programming.
      Our goal is to make coding fun, accessible, and practical for everyone.
    </p>

    <h2>What We Offer</h2>
    <p>
      Through our short programming courses, you'll learn the basics of HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. Whether you're
      aiming to build websites, apps, or just learn a valuable new skill, we're here to guide you every step of the way.
    </p>
  </section>

</body>
</html>
